item.title: ASX Shares Dive After Rival Cboe Challenges Market Dominance
item.description: ASX Ltd shares tumbled the most in two years as potential market competition from Cboe Global Markets Inc and regulatory issues weigh on Australia’s embattled main exchange operator.
